y Ride\" (season 3: episode 2)\n|-\n|2008\n| ''The Apostles''\n| Kelly Calhoun\n| Television movie\n|-\n| 2009\n| ''[[Knight Rider (2008 TV series)|Knight Rider]]''\n| Annie Ortiz\n|| 1 episode \"Fight Knight\" (season 1: episode 14)\n|-\n|2009\n| ''[[Without a Trace]]''\n| Holly Shepard\n| 1 episode \"Chameleon\" (season 7: episode 15)\n|-\n|2009\n| ''[[Fringe (TV series)|Fringe]]''\n| Junior FBI Agent Amy Jessup\n| 2 episodes \"[[A New Day in the Old Town]]\" (season 2: episode 1)<br />\"[[Night of Desirable Objects (Fringe)|Night of Desirable Objects]]\" (season 2: episode 2)\n|-\n|2009\n| ''[[The League]]''\n| Random Girl\n| 1 episode \"The Bounce Test\" (season 1: episode 2)\n|-\n| 2010\n| ''[[CSI: Miami]]''\n| Officer Leah Montoya\n| 1 episode \"Backfire\" (season 8: episode 20)\n|-\n|2010\n| ''[[The Boys & Girls Guide to Getting Down]]''\n| Dana\n| Television movie\n|-\n| 2011\u20132018\n| ''[[Suits (American TV series)|Suits]]''\n| [[Rachel Zane]]\n| Series regular (seasons 1\u20137), 108 episodes\n|-\n| 2012\n| ''[[Castle (TV series)|Castle]]''\n| Charlotte Boyd/Sleeping Beauty\n| 1 episode \"Once Upon a Crime\" (season 4: episode 17)\n|-\n| 2014\n| ''When Sparks Fly''\n| Amy Peterson\n| rowspan=2|[[Hallmark Channel]] television movies\n|-\n|2016\n|''Dater's Handbook''\n| Cassandra Brand\n|}\n\n===Film===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! class=\"unsortable\" | Notes\n|-\n| 2005\n| ''[[A Lot like Love]]''\n| Passenger on plane\n|\n|-\n|2010\n| [[Remember Me (2010 film)|''Remember Me'']]\n| Megan\n|\n|-\n|2010\n| ''[[Get Him to the Greek]]''\n| Tatiana\n| Uncredited\n|-\n|2010\n| ''The Candidate''\n| Kat\n| Short film\n|-\n| 2011\n| ''[[Horrible Bosses]]''\n| Jamie\n|\n|-\n| 2012\n| ''[[Dysfunctional Friends]]''\n| Terry\n|\n|-\n| 2013\n| ''[[Random Encounters (film)|Random Encounters]]''\n| Mindy\n| UK Title: ''[[Random Encounters (film)|A Random Encounter]]''\n|-\n| 2015\n| ''[[Anti-Social (film)|Anti-Social]]''\n| Kirsten\n|